<p><lb n="1"/><g type="unclassified"/> jak· vaum̃ jaṇa<!-- Ulā? --> vviḥ vvaḥ hiṇata (bhv)ai <unclear>tr</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ai</supplied>y· traḥ hulai taṅān· sruviṅ· a(th/dh)ān· namvyaḥ<!-- maybe numeral instead of ḥ? --> 
<lb n="2"/>ya jem̃ hyam̃k· vā pu lyam̃ śarvvāṇi rai paryaṁ<!-- paryam̃? --> traiya<!-- or is there a faint ·? --> <unclear>tm</unclear>ai Ikān· di rimvaṅ(·) bhan· mudaḥ<!-- maybe numeral instead of ḥ? -->  
<lb n="3"/><g type="unclassified"/> jak· jina<!-- dina? --> vā māḥ mantri bhāna ṅan· devī di jana<!-- rana? danda?  --> <unclear>y</unclear>ak· tam̃<!-- tā? kā? --> sevya<!-- AL read pe vya which she thought was error for pu vyā --> pak· ladā 
<lb n="4"/>paryam̃ traiy· vā tasrom̃ syā(ṁ) bhā{1} ṅan· di rimvum̃ṅ· (p/s)an· ra yāk· santoṣa dāk· si hla 
<lb n="5"/><g type="unclassified"/> daj·<!-- dadam̃? --> bhadhrāṇī<!-- probably rudrāṇī --> {1}nāśa<!-- paranāśa? --> hetu tum̃ nī yām̃ vatum̃ kunay· p<unclear>u</unclear>nar· mvūk· vrim̃ kañam̃ 
<lb n="6"/>si tmum̃ <unclear>j</unclear>em̃ deva jmai jem̃ deha ñum̃ (ū/rā)C· deha ñum̃ Aṅa(m̃) santāpa ndiy·<!-- sandiy?  --> dhilu 
<lb n="7"/><unclear><g type="unclassified"/></unclear> ku(bh)u pa(v)im̃ mvin·<!-- patimvin·? --> dharmma nīm̃ si kum̃ (t/m)vuk· yām̃ vatum̃ ni ṅan· manaḥ sānanda<!-- Ānanda? --> vrim̃ 
<lb n="8"/> (bh/c)ājo di rim̃ ṅan· satva Cim̃ si kum̃ (vā dhā)sī tmum̃ ya nan· jem̃ deva janma rim̃ 
<lb n="9"/><g type="unclassified"/> di bhvai traiy· kum̃ mvuk· yām̃ vatum̃ ka bhāsa{1} ya nāśa jīva riṁ rai hetu kum̃ 
<lb n="10"/>vrim̃ dhap· na tmu klāḥ tā<unclear>pa</unclear> tmum̃ tamā jem̃ devatā viśeṣa jmai jem̃ deha ñum̃
